This paper focuses on defect prediction, which is a software engineering problem, and evaluates the cost efficiency of different approaches. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses machine learning techniques to create prediction models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of different approaches, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
